WEBVTT

00:01.565 --> 00:02.828
[woman]
Previously onQueen Sugar:

00:02.872 --> 00:06.180
My mother taught me
to believe in what's good.

00:06.223 --> 00:07.616
You're good.

00:07.659 --> 00:09.705
-What's wrong, baby?
-That's Nova's doing.

00:09.748 --> 00:11.402
She spit in my face.

00:11.446 --> 00:13.056
I'm never going to forgive her.

00:13.100 --> 00:15.276
If you decide to run
you'll discover the Landrys

00:15.319 --> 00:17.234
are just the tip of the spear.

00:17.278 --> 00:18.148
This isn't allowed.

00:18.192 --> 00:19.628
You made more enemies in a day

00:19.671 --> 00:21.064
than I've made in a lifetime.

00:21.108 --> 00:22.805
My pops is my daddy.

00:22.848 --> 00:24.372
But she says he ain't
your real one.

00:24.415 --> 00:26.417
Is that why I look different
than you?

00:26.461 --> 00:28.245
As long as my heart is beatin',
Blue,

00:28.289 --> 00:29.246
I'm gonna be your daddy.

00:29.290 --> 00:30.552
I chose you.

00:38.212 --> 00:39.430
[Octavia]
Oh!

00:39.474 --> 00:42.694
Beautiful, as usual.

00:42.738 --> 00:44.087
It's not too buttoned up?

00:44.131 --> 00:47.090
It is a serious suit
for a serious woman.

00:47.134 --> 00:48.091
[sighs]

00:48.135 --> 00:49.614
Packed press day tomorrow.

00:49.658 --> 00:51.138
Hopefully my feet
can take it.

00:51.181 --> 00:52.835
Oh, comfort is overrated

00:52.878 --> 00:55.881
when you look as amazing
as you do right now.

00:55.925 --> 00:58.710
Oh, I've connected with some
colleagues here in Atlanta

00:58.754 --> 01:00.973
to help drum up more
highbrows in the press.

01:01.017 --> 01:03.933
And there's a shindig this week
at that new social club.

01:03.976 --> 01:06.196
Lots of notables
should be there.

01:06.240 --> 01:07.806
You stay plugged in.

01:07.850 --> 01:09.678
I can give my publicist a call
to get us on the list.

01:09.721 --> 01:12.724
Oh, but we are already VIP,
my queen.

